<br>
It's pretty late in the night, and I decide to head to bed and get soem sleep.  Wake up the next morning, login, and at the character screen, my character is naked.  This is when the unsettling feeling in my stomache starts.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I login, and find myself at my bind point, as if the res never happened.  I figured, the server reset to an earlier save, and start running back to solb, no biggie.<br>
<br>
I zone into solb, and go to where I died the night before.  There's no corpse.  Thinking maybe it was safespotted, I run back to zone in and take a look, there's no corpse.  At this point that feeling in my stomache is starting to grow,  heheeh.  I do a /corpse, and it says that I have no corpse in the zone.  I think I can say, that's the worst thing to have ever happened to any of my characters.<br>
